        p.text-muted.text-justify
          | We invite the web development and UX community from Austria and the entire world to Salzburg. Have a brilliant and safe conference where you can #[strong meet old and new friends] to expand your knowledge and horizon.
      .col-4
        span.fa-stack.fa-4x
          i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x.text-primary
          i.fa.fa-code.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
        h4.service-heading The Web
        p.text-muted.text-justify
          | Come and hear talks about the #[strong wide variety of web and UX topics] and its community so you can build better applications for more platforms, devices and humans. Yes – the web is definitely a great place to be in.
      .col-4
        span.fa-stack.fa-4x
          i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x.text-primary
          i.fa.fa-map-marker.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
